        </aside>

        <section class="content">

            <div class="ticker">
                *** WELCOME TO DJANGO CENTRAL! ***
            </div>

            <article class="box intro">
                <h2>☆ What is Django?</h2>

                <div class="intro-body">
                    <div class="dragon">🐉</div>

                    <p>
                        Django is a high-level Python web framework that encourages
                        rapid development and clean, pragmatic design. It takes care
                        of much of the hassle of web development, so you can focus
                        on writing your app without reinventing the wheel.
                        <a href="#">Open source</a>, free, and ridiculously productive.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="features">
                    <div>💾 <b>DRY</b><br>Don't Repeat Yourself</div>
                    <div>🧠 <b>MVT</b><br>Pattern for sanity</div>
                    <div>🗃️ <b>ORM</b><br>Databases made easy</div>
                    <div>🔐 <b>ADMIN</b><br>Auto-magical admin</div>
                    <div>🛡️ <b>SECURE</b><br>Sleep tight at night</div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <section class="box news">
                <h2>✪✪✪ DJANGO NEWS ✪✪✪</h2>

                <div class="news-grid">
                    <ul>
